---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Sauna Brand Reviews - Backyard Sauna Pro"
  description="Honest brand overviews and comparisons for the top outdoor sauna manufacturers, Almost Heaven, Dundalk, Harvia, Dynamic Saunas, and more."
  canonical="/brands"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Sauna Brand Reviews</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 mb-10">Who makes a good sauna, and who to avoid. Brand-by-brand breakdowns.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <a href="/brands/almost-heaven-sauna-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Almost Heaven Saunas</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">The most popular US barrel sauna brand, quality, value, and best models reviewed.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

      <a href="/brands/dundalk-leisurecraft-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Dundalk LeisureCraft</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Premium Canadian-made barrel saunas, thick clear cedar and 30+ year build quality reviewed.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

      <a href="/brands/harvia-sauna-heater-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Harvia Sauna Heaters</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">The world's most popular sauna heater brand. KIP, M3, Cilindro reviewed and sized for your room.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/brands/huum-sauna-heater-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">HUUM Sauna Heaters</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Estonian heaters with exceptional design, and the UL listing issue US buyers need to know.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

      <a href="/brands/finnleo-sauna-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Finnleo Saunas</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Premium Finnish brand with strong US dealer support. Who it's for and whether the price premium is worth it.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

      <a href="/brands/harvia-sauna-heater-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Harvia Sauna Heaters</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">The default heater recommendation for North American buyers. KIP, Cilindro, and M3 wood-burning models covered.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

      <a href="/brands/dynamic-saunas-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Dynamic Saunas</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">The top-rated plug-in infrared sauna brand. What they get right, where they cut corners, and which model to buy.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/brands/redwood-outdoors-sauna-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Redwood Outdoors</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Premium Thermowood barrel and cabin saunas. Better outdoor durability than cedar — is the premium worth it?</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/brands/finnish-sauna-builders-review" class="block bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow transition-all">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">Finnish Sauna Builders</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Specialty sauna retailer carrying Almost Heaven, Dundalk, and HUUM. Strong customer service — worth the slight premium?</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
